tal and theoretical results reported in\nthe literature for biaxial extensional flows of polymeric liquids.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Apr 2020 21:29:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 23 Apr 2020 08:28:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-24"}
