erical experiments demonstrate the\neffectiveness of our computable optimal expansions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Apr 2020 07:26:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 2 Nov 2020 01:53:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 3 Jan 2022 08:37:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-04"}
