pidly moving towards the rest wavelength. Importantly,\nthe absolute continuum intensity, ratio of component intensities, relative time\nof appearance, and red-shift amplitude, are sensitive to the model input\nparameters, showing great potential as diagnostics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Apr 2020 15:32:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-27"}
